## 🧮 Task 1 — DSA (Primary Focus)

⏰ Time: 1 hr

### 🧩 Problem

**287. Find the Duplicate Number**
🔗 https://leetcode.com/problems/find-the-duplicate-number/

### 📌 Focus

* Understand the problem constraints carefully
* Compare different approaches:

  * Brute Force
  * Frequency Array
  * Sorting
  * Floyd's Cycle Detection (Optimal)

### 📝 Write

* Why the duplicate can be viewed as a cycle
* Difference between Frequency Array and Floyd's Algorithm
* Time & Space Complexity of each approach

### ⚡ Expected Complexity (Optimal)

* Time Complexity: O(n)
* Space Complexity: O(1)

